code: @Bean public static MeterRegistryPostProcessor meterRegistryPostProcessor(ObjectProvider<MeterBinder> meterBinders, ObjectProvider<MeterFilter> meterFilters, ObjectProvider<MeterRegistryCustomizer<?>> meterRegistryCustomizers, ObjectProvider<MetricsProperties> metricsProperties) {     return new MeterRegistryPostProcessor(meterBinders, meterFilters, meterRegistryCustomizers, metricsProperties). }
